Package com.intellij.util.containers

Class ContainerUtilRt

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.util.containers.ContainerUtilRt
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContainerUtil

    public class ContainerUtilRt
extends java.lang.Object
    Stripped-down version of ContainerUtil. Intended to use by external (out-of-IDE-process) runners and helpers so it should not contain any library dependencies.
